I bleached my hair and that killed it. I had to start from ground zero after shaving my head. That being said I was so desperate for it to get long and fast. Everyone’s hair is different. The first year natural I rarely washed my hair and I started doing hair masks. I started avoiding sulfates and all those things. The 2nd year I tried out what products felt best for my hair and deep conditioned once a week regularly. I’m entering my 3rd year now and I’m past shoulder length about, i do nothing special these days. Just leaving it alone was the best decision
